\pard{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf4\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1\ulnone\b0\i\fs28 maintaing code conventions always help us to better understandability and  readability  of the source code.\i0\f1\fs22\par
