\pard{\pntext\f4\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf4\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\fi-360\li720\sa200\sl276\slmult1\qj\ul while Statements\ulnone\b\fs36 :\b0\fs28 A while statement should have the following form:\par

